{"tid":2369653,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：疫情之初對病毒乏認識，不能說是「漏招」","createTime":"2021-01-17T10:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T14:26:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5618671da176ff109a05476a99edf643f9cd8106","tid":2369653,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=420569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420569&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=3ee7b1c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420569&h=7f401766\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=420569</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】新冠病毒傳入本港至今一年，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始接受本台專訪，回顧抗疫366天，認為有時措施做慢了，只是因為當刻對病毒不認識，不能說是「漏招」，政府已經盡全力，把疫情控制到最好。<br />\n<br />\n去年一月二十三日，本港出現第一宗新冠肺炎確診，患者來自武漢，第一波疫情開始。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始：「我們最初對病毒不認識，根據以往經驗，衞生署提出探熱，有問題一定會發燒，加上健康申報，但這兩件事是否漏了，應該要做檢測？沒有人可以這樣說，因為當時大家對病毒都不認識。後來我們更了解病毒，知道有隱形患者，即其他（措施）都不夠，就要再加強。」<br />\n<br />\n隨後幾波疫情，均同輸入個案有關，政府要不斷堵塞防疫漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始：「有些預防不到，有些一定要應對，不等於應對就是『漏招』。」<br />\n<br />\n為了控制本地疫情擴散，政府做了很多「第一次」，包括限聚令、口罩令、禁堂食，關處所，還有社區檢測中心、臨時興建的檢疫中心、社區治療設施等等。為了抗疫，巿民的自由少了，對政府的怨氣多了。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始：「當然任何事都要平衡，若市民感覺私隱被侵犯，我們政府做事都很小心。任何政治化討論，對防疫抗疫沒有幫助。我們從公共衞生角度，大家都說是戰時思維。」<br />\n<br />\n一年過去，確診人數累計近萬人，160多人死亡，作為領導這場抗疫戰的問責官員，陳肇始認為自己己經盡了力。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始：「（這是政府控制到最低的數字？是否已盡全力？）我們一定是盡了全力。（一年抗疫中，你評自己多少分？）我想評分很難自己評分給自己。我們在全面抗疫，政府上上下下食衞局和其他局，和其他政府同事，包括前線醫護人員，大家都盡了很大努力。」"},{"pid":"fa89fbca6e2c587c8acdc7ed3c3f549c58b1f38b","tid":2369653,"uid":177047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"佢不如話係佢想像力太差<br />\n<br />\n陳護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefb00764c2e37da5db6c73e077fbda3cb2c4919","tid":2369653,"uid":77453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:24:57.000Z","msg":"漏左成年 重漏緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6904645123f332d84c9fa679bb2dd152c5f39e0f","tid":2369653,"uid":217257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"台灣表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e73319409eba2dafa20fc4ea251ce31c7e1a17","tid":2369653,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"點解無多謝中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f29cec747431a7f430d6ffc3727eed712c0560a","tid":2369653,"uid":277088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:29:26.000Z","msg":"沙士既經驗仲唔夠認識?"},{"pid":"4ec9769c2755b701f7c0eb2e712bcf58f4a39922","tid":2369653,"uid":47202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:31:20.000Z","msg":"總之政府就做乜都啱，所有問題都係市民既錯。"},{"pid":"c5f5b4d20c88f7a3d7499b7415d55d2a224a6ab4","tid":2369653,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6904645123f332d84c9fa679bb2dd152c5f39e0f","tid":2369653,"uid":217257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"台灣表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:31:54.000Z","msg":"澳門"},{"pid":"f95462b9245f50a57affcd83bf975c0cdbb8f73e","tid":2369653,"uid":42034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"曲線屌9中國隱瞞疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fa5a8c302ed1dc4b5603402035b8d8431a8c8c","tid":2369653,"uid":292227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:33:19.000Z","msg":"而家就好撚熟囉，番工搭車六點前唔攪你，遊行娛樂6點後就出動嘛吊"},{"pid":"4a5860cd6da5993e53c20ec7385c2fdd728acf07","tid":2369653,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"孔乙己真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗疫的事能算是漏招麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20ebf85a3ee9941dfa286865add93fd600163f7","tid":2369653,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f95462b9245f50a57affcd83bf975c0cdbb8f73e","tid":2369653,"uid":42034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"曲線屌9中國隱瞞疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"你諗多左，佢只係話自己已經做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5d5e47d06497abe1c98e57ba250a7bc8608002","tid":2369653,"uid":268146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"疫情去到第四波，學曉左未？"},{"pid":"8a2c21d82510015f5ab7748660612e17326cd813","tid":2369653,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"汁都漏埋添啦"},{"pid":"84ef5d7f032dbf31757f395e9333cab7bf4786c2","tid":2369653,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"唔可以怪我<br />\n=我冇錯<br />\n=冇人有錯<br />\n=冇人要負責<br />\n<br />\n你班蟻民聽明未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11dd6146118a84dd6a0a45ad50f983ded15f17e8","tid":2369653,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"市民預防唔到一個失敗嘅極權"},{"pid":"f46f9163b7e13fddb63b657d61ff49da3afd2828","tid":2369653,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n叫你封關，為嘅係堵截源頭<br />\n呢樣嘢同你對武漢肺炎認唔認識，冇咩關係架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid